(400009,2,'常用开发库 - 其它常用类库','想了解哪个常用类库用的最多？ 看这里搜索吧: Maven 仓库在新窗口打开https://mvnrepository.com/open-source 比如Http Clients库 原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/develop/package/dev-package-x-others.html','# 常用开发库 - 其它常用类库\n\n> 其它常用类库体系很庞大，但是工具类的原则是只需要查找会使用即可。@pdai\n\n## 常用类库资源\n\n想了解哪个常用类库用的最多？ 看这里搜索吧: [Maven 仓库在新窗口打开](https://mvnrepository.com/open-source)\n\n![图片](/api/uploads/files/pdai/dev-package-others-1-34d006d1fd.png)\n\n比如Http Clients库\n\n![图片](/api/uploads/files/pdai/dev-package-others-2-516b11e23b.png)\n\n## 搜索常用\n\n> 还想看看国内一些比较好的开源的？[https://gitee.com/explore在新窗口打开](https://gitee.com/explore)\n\n![图片](/api/uploads/files/pdai/dev-package-common-4-82a0d2fbd6.png)\n\n## 参考\n\n- https://mvnrepository.com/open-source\n- https://gitee.com/explore\n\n---\n\n原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/develop/package/dev-package-x-others.html','https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1519389950473-47ba0277781c?w=800','开发之常用类库',NULL,0,NULL,'pdai-develop-package-dev-package-x-others','常用开发库 - 其它常用类库 - 技术博客','想了解哪个常用类库用的最多？ 看这里搜索吧: Maven 仓库在新窗口打开https://mvnrepository.com/open-source 比如Http Clients库 原文链接：https://pdai.tech/md/dev...',0,'PUBLISHED',5766,281,129,58,'2025-06-28 00:00:00','2025-06-28 00:00:00','2026-05-08 23:23:19',NULL,0) ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE `author_id`=VALUES(`author_id`),`title`=VALUES(`title`),`summary`=VALUES(`summary`),`content`=VALUES(`content`),`cover_url`=VALUES(`cover_url`),`category`=VALUES(`category`),`offline_reason`=VALUES(`offline_reason`),`featured`=VALUES(`featured`),`featured_at`=VALUES(`featured_at`),`seo_title`=VALUES(`seo_title`),`seo_description`=VALUES(`seo_description`),`warn_flag`=VALUES(`warn_flag`),`status`=VALUES(`status`),`view_count`=VALUES(`view_count`),`like_count`=VALUES(`like_count`),`favorite_count`=VALUES(`favorite_count`),`comment_count`=VALUES(`comment_count`),`published_at`=VALUES(`published_at`),`updated_at`=VALUES(`updated_at`),`deleted_at`=NULL;
